com.zepl.challenge.data

Class ImmutableToDo.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zepl.challenge.data.ImmutableToDo.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ImmutableToDo

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ImmutableToDo.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of type ImmutableToDo. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
